dct_title_s: Greece after the Doric migration, 1000-900 B.C.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Insets: Plain of Troy -- Greece in the heroic age (scale 1:5,000,000). At head of map: Dr. William Smith's Ancient atlas. 20. Plate 20 from: Atlas of ancient geography, biblical and classical ... / edited by William Smith and George Grove. London : J. Murray, 1874. Historic Maps copy imperfect: Lower margin of map wanting, with lost of text. Author and imprint suggested by plate 21.
